CGI-Carp-DebugScreen version 0.04
=================================

CGI::Carp::DebugScreen provides decent debug/error screens for Web
applications via CGI::Carp's set_message() function. You don't need
to care $SIG{__DIE__} anymore. Just die or croak to get the right 
thing. You can customize those screens as well.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  CGI::Carp

